color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:22.0000pt;" ><font face="黑体" >项目总览</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:黑体;color:rgb(0,0,0);
mso-ansi-font-weight:normal;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:22.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></h1><p class=MsoBodyText  style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;
font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >核心定位</font> <font face="宋体" >纯人脉资源对接</font> / <font face="宋体" >需求匹配 </font><font face="Times New Roman" >/ </font><font face="宋体" >居间举荐的信息撮合平台。坚守</font><font face="Times New Roman" >“</font><font face="宋体" >千君万码</font><font face="Times New Roman" >&#183;</font><font face="宋体" >码上有钱</font><font face="Times New Roman" >”</font><font face="宋体" >理念，汇聚正人君子（杜绝骗子小人），汇聚合规优质用户与二维码资源；实现</font><font face="Times New Roman" >“</font><font face="宋体" >许愿方</font><font face="Times New Roman" >-</font><font face="宋体" >能量供给方</font><font face="Times New Roman" >-</font><font face="宋体" >举荐人</font><font face="Times New Roman" >”</font><font face="宋体" >三方闭环，提供保证金认证机制，保障合作安全；不参与任何交易行为，仅记录资金流水，不触碰用户资金。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;
font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoBodyText  style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;
font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >多端支持</font> <font face="宋体" >微信小程序</font> + <font face="宋体" >独立站（</font><font face="Times New Roman" >PC/</font><font face="宋体" >手机</font><font face="Times New Roman" >/Pad</font><font face="宋体" >）共用同一后台，数据实时同步。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;
font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoBodyText  style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;
font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >适用人群</font> <font face="宋体" >有需求的个人</font>/<font face="宋体" >企业、拥有行业</font><font face="Times New Roman" >/</font><font face="宋体" >部门人脉者、拥有企业人脉者、举荐人、平台管理员。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;
font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoBodyText  style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;
font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >核心原则</font> <font face="宋体" >所有核心逻辑后端自动化，前端仅展示与交互；坚守主权合规（官方标准地图）、内容合规（敏感词过滤）、资金合规（第三方支付流转）；后台配置灵活，无需技术介入；敏感信息加密存储，操作日志全程可追溯。每个用户操作均有默认提醒（解释文案后台可编辑）。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;
font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><h1 style="margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:0.0000pt;
mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l12 level1 lfo2;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:黑体;mso-ascii-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:16.0000pt;
