font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >项目交流区所有消息永久留存，拍板人可终止项目，终止后不可再推进合同。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;
font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoBodyText  style="margin-left:36.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:blank 36.0000pt ;
