font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="宋体" >收益分成比例写死：一级居间人</font>60%<font face="宋体" >，二级居间人</font><font face="Times New Roman" >40%</font><font face="宋体" >（中间人内部），但项目层级的办事人</font><font face="Times New Roman" >/</font><font face="宋体" >中间人比例可由发起人设定（默认</font><font face="Times New Roman" >80/20</font><font face="宋体" >）。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;
font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoBodyText  style="margin-left:36.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:blank 36.0000pt ;
